fields.value: Mouse-brain vasculature, ventral side. LSFM acquisition.

dsDescriptionValue.value: Zipped files containing single stacks of half mouse-brain corresponding to the ventral side. The planes of each stack go from the inside of the brain towards the surface of the ventral side. Voxel size 0.65x0.65x2 um (x,y,z). Nominal overlap between stacks = 300 um for each side. Acquisition with LSFM.

publicationCitation.value: Whole-brain vasculature reconstruction at the single capillary level
